~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   Command~RS  : csay                                      ~FTPODnuts
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

~FT   Usage~RS    : csay <roomname> <message>

   Will make one of your clones in the given room speak. If you see 
   something nasty being said in the clones room its an alternative to 
   shouting, telling or actually going to the room to admonish the 
   miscreant.

~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   See also~RS : clone, destroy, allclones, myclones, chear, switch
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
